{"tid":500603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以巴衝突持續 四名巴人中槍身亡百多人受傷","createTime":"2017-12-16T02:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T10:50:23.000Z","uid":20816,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9d9467c15c59d0d2b0988d979164260d563fefda","tid":500603,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:54:39.000Z","msg":"巴勒斯坦民眾繼續示威，抗議美國承認耶路撒冷為以色列首都，四名巴人中槍死亡，百多人受傷。  二千多名巴人在西岸示威，抗議美國承認耶路撒冷為以色列首都。  示威者向軍警投擲燃燒彈和石頭，焚燒車胎，以軍施放催淚氣體及開槍還擊。  有示威者中槍由救護車送院，據報他身上藏有炸彈，以色列指他企圖用刀襲擊軍警。  在加沙邊境附近，同樣有數千名巴人上街，與以軍衝突，數十名巴人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5a340aaee60383622881f272/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5a340aaee60383622881f272%2F&d=UQDAp1wca%2FgJo0Q%2BgRQ5ajCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9e33e546\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5a340aaee60383622881f272/</a>"},{"pid":"a49519585712ca14f7333f3fc4cd07ad7db471be","tid":500603,"uid":20816,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:06:52.000Z","msg":"殺晒d恐怖份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9685693dd5914df5d671199b29d78d3a916818","tid":500603,"uid":20816,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:18:14.000Z","msg":"支持以色列支持當撈侵"},{"pid":"ebb3c918b48f20eb253432a01892a7f4443663b5","tid":500603,"uid":48631,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:20:36.000Z","msg":"殺鳩晒班巴人就啱架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25249a8bb3dcb3e20222f4719d3832cddd06da8","tid":500603,"uid":102096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:21:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d99cbd06624e70ee995d18fcaa96c5f6b07c0679","tid":500603,"uid":34410,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"殺哂D回豬就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b46d5b48f33644518aee16b74baadfdc